About Us

Learn more about TruPath Specialty Vehicles

Our Story

Founded with a vision to transform the specialty vehicle industry, TruPath Specialty Vehicles has grown to become a leading manufacturer of work trucks, specialty vehicles, and buses tailored to meet the unique needs of our customers.

At TruPath, we combine innovative design with superior craftsmanship to create vehicles that exceed expectations in performance, durability, and value. Our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction has made us a trusted partner for businesses, municipalities, and organizations across the country.

With decades of combined experience, our team understands the complex requirements of specialty vehicles and is dedicated to delivering solutions that help our customers succeed.

Our Core Values

Excellence

We strive for excellence in everything we do, from design and manufacturing to customer service.

Innovation

We continuously innovate to provide cutting-edge solutions that address evolving customer needs.

Integrity

We conduct business with the highest level of integrity, transparency, and ethical standards.

Customer Focus

We are dedicated to understanding and meeting our customers' unique requirements and expectations.

Ready to work with us?

Contact our team to discuss your specialty vehicle needs or find a dealer near you.
